{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/Start.png?t=1738019854\" />Ghost Catcher is a cooperative horror game that can be played by at least 1 and up to 8 players together. You need to continuously delve into the haunted house, unlock new areas, uncover the truth behind the case; conduct mysterious rituals, confront spiritual entities, identify their types, and ultimately capture them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u65b0\u5e7b\u5316\u732b\u54aa\u7684\u80fd\u529b.gif?t=1738019854\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u5e7b\u5316\u732b\u54aa\u7684\u80fd\u529b.png?t=1738019854\" />In the game, players can transform into adorable kittens, not only to evade the hunting of spiritual entities but also to discover hidden items through special vision. They can even interact with other players, enjoying the fun of lazing around.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u65b0\u4e0d\u65ad\u53d8\u5316\u7684\u5730\u56fe.gif?t=1738019854\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u4e0d\u65ad\u53d8\u5316\u7684\u5730\u56fe.png?t=1738019854\" />Search for clues in the map to increase exploration, learn more about the stories hidden in the shadows, unlock broader activity areas, add advanced gameplay, until the entire map is explored and the spiritual entities nesting there are completely subdued, to gain achievements and special rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u6bcf\u5c40\u4e0d\u540c\u7684\u4f53\u9a8c.gif?t=1738019854\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u6bcf\u5c40\u4e0d\u540c\u7684\u4f53\u9a8c.png?t=1738019854\" />Each entry will confront different spiritual entities, completely random cursed items and relics, as well as a variety of map events that need to be resolved, ensuring that each game session is a unique experience, with endless challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u60ca\u609a\u7535\u5f71\u98ce\u683c\u7684\u573a\u666f.gif?t=1738019854\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u60ca\u609a\u7535\u5f71\u98ce\u683c\u7684\u573a\u666f.png?t=1738019854\" />If you're tired of playing house in the same old apartments and crave a more thrilling adventure, a series of diverse and distinct dungeons, including farms and the upcoming amusement park, are waiting for your conquest</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u5f62\u5f62\u8272\u8272\u7684\u88c5\u626e.gif?t=1738019854\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u5f62\u5f62\u8272\u8272\u7684\u88c5\u626e.png?t=1738019854\" />Here you can see enchanting demons flaunting themselves, holy nuns standing guard in assistance, and even beautiful pharaohs accompanying you. However, to attract more attention, perhaps using a mix-and-match style to showcase yourself is also a good option, it's up to your preference</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u65b0\u8d34\u8fd1\u771f\u5b9e\u7684\u753b\u9762.gif?t=1738019854\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/\u8d34\u8fd1\u771f\u5b9e\u7684\u753b\u9762.png?t=1738019854\" />Meticulously crafted using Unreal Engine 5 for better visual expressiveness, dedicated to providing players with a stronger sense of immersion, and experiencing the most immersive exorcism journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/7.png?t=1738019854\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Newcomer getting started","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2334450/493866f46fbc67cf4aba020c4ad24f39f9af33eb.jpg"},{"name":"Industry elite","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2334450/619dba948b415011504bdaac1cae82c44115a6b4.jpg"},{"name":"Rookie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2334450/0613f69cba50839d3586c31e5b8212b5aa343281.jpg"},{"name":"Elite","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2334450/11ad7dd532a13cf7120dbc706309fb83ca022fdc.jpg"},{"name":"Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2334450/14e9f98802a1852f8ba0f3c45b13d8cb7fec4fb2.jpg"},{"name":"First bucket of gold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2334450/e64cb2f8e6aad30f75308846ce8fd7da7e061fa5.jpg"},{"name":"Abundant financial resources","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2334450/18c54ea2afe5fd291d79b1b3848de35c10c40c8a.jpg"},{"name":"Rich enough to rival a nation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2334450/298d200f3501a8a401b26eae1723df3da1aca3ac.jpg"},{"name":"I am a le